1043
01:00:31,560 --> 01:00:34,880
- Y'all get off of me! Get off of me!
- Don't trip out on me right now.

1044
01:00:35,080 --> 01:00:37,760
Do anybody know
where this air-conditioning unit is?

1045
01:00:38,240 --> 01:00:41,120
Hold up. Let me get that light.

1046
01:00:41,480 --> 01:00:43,000
Come on, give it up.

1047
01:00:46,320 --> 01:00:50,160
You're supposed to be fixing
the air conditioner, not taking a tour.

1048
01:00:50,360 --> 01:00:51,720
I know.

1049
01:00:51,880 --> 01:00:53,360
Let's go.

1050
01:00:55,600 --> 01:00:59,560
First, we got to look for this money
in one more place.

